Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.24,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走出黑暗 重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直至光芒 照亮结局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑恶嘴脸 咒骂不止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.45,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:03.17,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:09.93,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童绞尽脑汁 只为保护手中硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:16.43,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:23.44,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童手中 紧攥最后一枚硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.40,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毁灭与重生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.45,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.26,op-en,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:46.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's start a new life from the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.32,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Until the light reveals the end
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:53.12,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sinister faces, growing curses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.45,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my last war
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:03.17,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels playing disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:09.93,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:16.43,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:23.44,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.40,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.45,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
